== Alpha

Start console: forman run rails console
Start app: foreman start

git clone git://github.com:activefx/alpha.git
rename alpha <new_application_name>
git remote rename origin alpha
bundle install
rake development:install
git commit -a -m 'installed alpha'

Requires PhantomJS for guard-jasmine testing
See http://railscasts.com/episodes/261-testing-javascript-with-jasmine-revised

# Build PhantomJS from source
  sudo apt-get install libqt4-dev libqtwebkit-dev qt4-qmake
  git clone git://github.com/ariya/phantomjs.git && cd phantomjs
  git checkout 1.3
  qmake-qt4 && make

